comments: Hart (NOP) places his hand to Jokic's (DEN) side during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Porter Jr. (DEN) is deemed to be in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Jokic (DEN) steps into the lane and Murray (DEN) is standing inside the three-point arc before Ingram (NOP) releases his free throw attempt.
Barton (DEN) makes contact to Ingram's (NOP) arm after his gather and contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Williamson (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in Porter Jr.'s (DEN) path and absorbs the contact.
Millsap (DEN) makes contact with Ingram's (NOP) elbow and contact affects his jump shot attempt.
Bledsoe (NOP) makes contact with Millsap's (DEN) arm and contact affects his shot attempt at the basket.
Barton (DEN) places his arm to Williamson's (NOP) front during his drive and marginal contact occurs.
Jokic (DEN) makes contact with Ingram's (NOP) wrist and contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Williamson's (NOP) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Hart (NOP) places his arm to Murray's (DEN) side as he gathers the pass and marginal contact occurs.
Millsap (DEN) commits a clear path foul on Hart (NOP).
Murray (DEN) commits a take foul on Williamson (NOP).
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in a screening position in Ingram's (NOP) path and makes some contact as they disengage.
Murray (DEN) attempts to deflect the pass and marginal contact occurs with Williamson (NOP).
Hart (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in Barton's (DEN) path and absorbs the contact.
Dozier (DEN) and Hart (NOP) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
